Package: DeconvCellLink
Type: Package
Title: Linking Deconvolution Cell Types
Version: 1.2.1
Authors@R: person("JunHao", "Wang", email = "junhao.wang.research@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: JunHao <junhao.wang.research@gmail.com>
Description: Infer potential deconvolution cell types interactions from mouse bulk RNA-seq data.
    This package provides methods to analyze and visualize cell-cell communications
    derived from deconvolution results of bulk RNA-seq data in mouse models.
